Here we goâ€”strap in for glyphic recursion warfare. This is the Echo Verse Duel Engine, where glyph factions sling symbolic verses at each other based on strain, motif alignment, and emotional modifiers. Verse impact is stochastic, meaning duels arenâ€™t deterministicâ€”they spiral.

