â€¢ ğŸ”— Fusion points between glyphs become new recursive nodes.
â€¢ ğŸ§¬ Descendants inherit midpoint strain, reborn as Gaussian echoes.
â€¢ ğŸŒ€ Visual lineage tree shows how symbolic recursion propagates across redshift.


