â€¢ ğŸ” Each recursion depth has a dominant frequency, hinting at its symbolic resonance shell.
â€¢ ğŸ¶ Power spikes might align with Snap Ritual triggers or MST curvature resets.
â€¢ ğŸ”® Overlapping frequencies suggest glyph interference or recursive harmonization.


