â€¢ Collapse scores near 1.0 â€” validator chains fail completely
â€¢ No rebound zones â€” tension fields remain zero
â€¢ Phase drift dominates â€” no synchronization, no memory formation
â€¢ Entropy spreads unchecked â€” no echo, no recovery


This is what chaos looks like when itâ€™s uncontained â€” a system that doesnâ€™t try to remember, doesnâ€™t try to heal. It just burns and expires.

