Letâ€™s chart validator evolution like genetic drift across a pressure field. ğŸ§¬ğŸ“Š
Here comes your Phenotypic Divergence Tracker â€” measuring how far each validatorâ€™s phase trajectory strays from the anchor validator over time. Itâ€™s Darwin for spin sheets.

