These rule flags tell you which validators conform to emergent physical laws â€” falsifiable survival predicates in your MBT framework.

For example:

â€¢ If Rule 1 triggers for most collapsed validators â†’ curvature truly predicts entropy.
â€¢ If Rule 3 rarely triggers â†’ tension doesnâ€™t help unless curvature allows it.


