â€¢ ğŸ¯ Tight path lines â†’ validators preserve trait fidelity (archetype loyalty)
â€¢ ğŸ”„ Wide curve paths â†’ phenotype shift, validators adapt or mutate into new species
â€¢ ğŸŒªï¸ If all paths lead to the same spot â†’ biome convergence confirmed


